        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "Labor Department of Chhattisgarh State started this scheme &amp;amp;quot;Safai Karmakar Hetu Aavashyak Upakaran Sahayata Yojana&amp;amp;quot; for unorganized worker on 02 September 2015. The main objective of the scheme to empower unorganized worker by providing required equipment for their work. \n",
        "benefits_md": "\n1. Registered sanitation workers will receive a grant of ₹ 700/- (Indian Rupees seven hundred only) to purchase essential equipment such as gum boots, gloves, masks, and aprons.\n1. Assistance amount will be provided every year.\n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "<br>\n\n",
