          "process_md": "**Unregistered Applicant :**\n\n1. All the applicant have to visit the official [website](https://cglabour.nic.in) Chhattisgarh Labour Department. 1. On the home page click on &quot;[Apply](https://cglabour.nic.in/Departments.aspx?id=4)&quot; under &quot;Chhattisgarh Unorganized Workers State Social Security Board&quot;.1. Enter the following details\n\n   1. Select Group Name : &quot;Asangathit Marmakaar Mandal&quot;\n   1. Select Service : &quot;Asangathit Shramik Panjikaran&quot;\n   1. What do you want to do :  &quot;Aavedan&quot;\n   1. Click next.\n\n1. Check the eligibility criteria for registration in Chhattisgarh Unorganized Workers State Social Security Board and click next. \n1. Fill out the online &quot;Registration form&quot;.\n1. Submit.\n\n<br>\n\n<br>\n\n**Already Registered Applicant :**\n\n1. All the applicant have to visit the official [website](https://cglabour.nic.in) Chhattisgarh Labour Department. 1. On the home page click on &quot;[Apply](https://cglabour.nic.in/Departments.aspx?id=4)&quot; under &quot;Chhattisgarh Unorganized Workers State Social Security Board&quot;.1. Enter the following details\n\n   1. Select Group Name : &quot;Asangathit Marmakaar Mandal&quot;\n   1. Select Service : &quot;Yojana&quot;\n   1. What do you want to do :  &quot;Aavedan&quot;\n   1. Click next.\n\n1. Select your district name and provide old/new registration number and click next.\n1. Select the scheme name. \n1. Fill out the online with required details. \n1. Submit.\n\n"
        }
